name: Going in Blind with Zach Tidwell

episodes.title: #32 Eric Ham: Escaping the Jehovah's Witnesses
episodes.description:
Eric Ham was raised  as a Jehovah’s Witness, but extracted himself from that environment as a teen following an experience that shook the foundations of his faith. Listen to the uncomfortable truths he feels responsible to share with the world.
 
You can find Eric at his Brazilian Jiu-Jitsu gym in Austing, Texas—Austin Jiu-Jitsu Collective, or in the following places:
